# Artificial Intelligence and Open RAN

## Overview

This assignment examined how Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning improve Open RAN by enabling intelligent resource allocation, predictive maintenance, and Self-Organizing Networks (SON).

## Technologies

- AI
- Machine Learning
- Open RAN
- RIC

## Skills Developed

- AI in telecommunications
- Intelligent network management
- Open RAN architecture

## Learning Outcome

This project demonstrated how AI can automate and optimize wireless communication networks.
